Who's this?

Hi, I’m Matthew. I’m a product designer, frontend developer, maker of all things digital, working remotely from Manchester, UK. Right now I’m working on my side projects, while looking for a long-term product I could get stuck into. If you are working on one and looking for a product designer, get in touch. Recently, I’ve made sharedthis.email, a platform for publishing emails. Feel free to check out my other side projects. I’m most active as @matthewmorek on Twitter, where I share stuff I work on and tweet about design and development. You can also find me on GitHub where I experiment with code.

What can you do?

Here are some of the things I can do. I spend a lot of time learning things that help me grow as a designer and developer.
